membership:
ELRA is a institutional observer in the European Judicial Network (EJN). &#xd;
&#xd;
ELRA is also member of the European Law Institute &#xd;
http://www.europeanlawinstitute.eu/&#xd;
&#xd;
ELRA signed in 2013 a Memorandum of Understanding with IPRA-CINDER. In 2012 a Memorandum of Understanding (Common Vision document) with CLGE, PCC, EuroGeographics, EULIS and FIG.

